<table><tr><td>American Geriatrics Society 2015 Beers Criteria Update Expert Panel. American Geriatrics Society 2015 updated Beers Criteria for potentially inappropriate medication use in older adults. J Am Geriatr Soc. 2015 Nov;63(11):2227-46. [42 references] <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180712203659/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=26446832" target="_blank">PubMed</a> <img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712203659im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712203659/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=49933&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%252fdoi%252f10.1111%252fjgs.13702%252fpdf">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712203659im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
    </div>
