                <li>TCAs </li>
                <li>Vincristine </li>
            </ul>
            </td>
            <td valign="top">May exacerbate or cause syndrome of inappropriate antidiuretic hormone secretion or hyponatremia; monitor sodium level closely when starting or changing dosages in older adults</td>
